{"word":"H8248 - שָׁקָה - shâqâh - shaw-kaw' - Cause to drink","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁקָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâqâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cause to drink"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - புஷ்டியாயிரு, குடி, நனை, நீர்ப்பாய்ச்சு, பாய், தண்ணீர்பானம் கொடு, தாகம், பானம் கொடு, பானபாத்திரக் காரன், பெருவெள்ளமாகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to give to drink, to irrigate, to drink, to water, to cause to drink water"},{"paragraph":"a) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to water, to irrigate"},{"paragraph":"2) to water, to give drink to"},{"paragraph":"b) (Pual) to be watered"},{"paragraph":"c) (Niphal) a variant"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>quaff</i>, that is, (causatively) to <i>irrigate</i> or <i>furnish a potion</i> to: - cause to (give, give to, let, make to) drink, drown, moisten, water. See <a href=\"#/H7937 - שָׁכַר - shâkar - shaw-kar'/7937\">H7937</a>, <a href=\"#/H8354 - שָׁתָה - shâthâh - shaw-thaw'/8354\">H8354</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4945 - מַשְׁקֶה - mashqeh - mash-keh'/4945\">H4945</a>, <a href=\"#/H8248 - שָׁקָה - shâqâh - shaw-kaw'/8248\">H8248</a>, <a href=\"#/H8249 - שִׁקֻּו - shiqquv - shif-koov'/8249\">H8249</a>, <a href=\"#/H8250 - שִׁקּוּי - shiqqûwy - shik-koo'-ee/8250\">H8250</a>, <a href=\"#/H8268 - שֹׁקֶת - shôqeth - sho'-keth/8268\">H8268</a>"}]}